RESUMO-CV.TEXTO-RESUMO-CV-RH:
Profissional com experincia na gesto de times para os mais variados projetos em empresas de grande porte no segmento de sade suplementar e tecnologia. Vivncia na criao de produtos (tecnologia), inovao, transformao digital, implantao de sistemas e criao de novos negcios.

Trabalha(ou) na liderana de diversos times como: infra estrutura, desenvolvimento de sistemas, suporte, outsorcing, implantao, migrao de dados, BI, cincia de dados, planejamento e LGPD.

Habilidade em negociar e interagir com outras reas. Com viso sistmica e do negcio na sade, j aceitou desafios de ser o head interino na nas seguintes reas: financeiro, planejamento estratgico, projetos e oramento.

A Formao em Cincia da Computao permitiu gerar experincia nas reas de desenvolvimento de software. MBA em Finanas Empresariais possibilita a interpretao de objetivos econmicos e financeiros. Mestrado em Computao, com nfase na Inteligncia Artificial, permite criar novos negcios e otimizar recursos para esta era da computao.

Considerado um "lder estrategista e executor" pela avaliao do processo de coaching executivo (2019) e premiado como destaque de turma no curso de "Executive High performance" (2017).
RESUMO-CV.TEXTO-RESUMO-CV-RH-EN:
Professional with experience in managing teams for the most varied projects in large companies in the supplementary health and technology segment. Experience in product creation (technology), innovation, digital transformation, systems implementation and creation of new businesses.

He works (or) in the leadership of several teams such as: infrastructure, systems development, support, outsorcing, implementation, data migration, BI, data science, planning and LGPD.

Ability to negotiate and interact with other areas. With a systemic and business vision in health, he has already accepted challenges of being the interim head in the following areas: finance, strategic planning, projects and budget.

Training in Computer Science allowed to generate experience in the areas of software development. MBA in Corporate Finance enables the interpretation of economic and financial objectives. Master in Computing, with an emphasis on Artificial Intelligence, allows you to create new businesses and optimize resources for this era of computing.

Considered a "strategist and executor leader" for the evaluation of the executive coaching process (2019) and awarded as a class highlight in the "Executive High performance" course (2017).
